We utilize open source tools to create an application, including both a web and phone based interface.

The Minimum Viable Product includes:

Tour guide locator,
Search features by city and region, Categories and recommended tours for art, music, food, sightseeing, historical events… Payment system, including customer service, Log in through other services such as Google, Facebook, and Twitter. Second and third generation updates to include: A built in one-stop-shop itinerary with sharable calendar, Linking tool to resources such as Expedia, Kayak, and Priceline, Push notifications, On-line chat rooms, Bundled destinations for economy travelers, Voice messaging for those less technologically inclined, (or people who have big thumbs, or less the optimal eye sight), Even more features and benefits to come…
